<p>Ahoy! Welcome to the Site News Automator! Below is a series of templates and tools designed to take some of the strain off setting up the monthly news.</p>
<h1 id="toc0"><span>Step 1: News Skeleton (doot doot)</span></h1>
<p>Copy this template and paste it in your sandbox. The dates will have to be changed monthly.</p>
